Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:04.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}空梦一场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}宿于右手的空虚记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于无人知晓的世界尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:16.61,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}被无尽的雨水打湿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:22.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}守护想要守护之物的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:27.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}无法相信这一切的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:32.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}接受一切 探求明日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}勇敢之光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}伸出手去你会见到光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:46.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}遍体伤痕的你会看到我的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:50.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}于高举的剑尖处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}将思绪交织
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:59.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}心愿超越时空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:05.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你的勇敢之光
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==================== OPJP ====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:59.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}左手に隠した願いは願いのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:04.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}冴えない夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:07.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}右手には空の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}誰も知らない世界の果て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:16.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}止まない雨に打たれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:22.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}守りたいものを守れる強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:27.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}それを信じられなくなるひ弱さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:32.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}すべてを受け入れて　明日を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:35.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Brave Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}手を伸ばせばnow you see the light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:46.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}傷だらけにnow you see my light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:50.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}翳した刃の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}思いを重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:59.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}祈りは時を超えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:05.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Your brave shine
