Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:58.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}如果心终会消失不再
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:14.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:19.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:27.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}都不过是生命梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.54,0:23:30.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:35.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:41.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:47.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:52.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:58.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耀眼的丘陵 必能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:04.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你所在的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:10.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}奏响你的心铃
